{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-asking-about-a-company/task-4","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"es-a1-learn-asking-about-a-company","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U ovoj vežbi, Sebastián pita za ulogu Elene unutar kompanije.</p>\n<p>Pitanje počinje sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿En qué...?</span>, što se često koristi za upit o <strong>specifičnoj oblasti, kategoriji ili sektoru</strong>.</p>\n<p>Slušaj zvukove i posmatraj promene glagola:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿En qué departamento trabajas?</span> - U kom odeljenju radite?</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Trabajas</span> koristi se u pitanju. Ovo je vrsta glagola koja odgovara drugoj licu jednine (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">tú</span>).</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Trabajo</span> Upotrebljava se u odgovoru. Ovo je vrsta glagola za prvo lice jedmine (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">yo</span>). Primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Trabajo en el departamento de diseño y experiencia de usuario.</span> - Radim u odeljenju za dizajn i korisničko iskustvo.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Trabajo en el departamento de diseño y experiencia de usuario</span> - Radim u odeljenju za dizajn i korisničko iskustvo.</p>\n<p>Glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">trabajo</span> (\"nafanya kazi\") završava se sa <strong>-o</strong>, što ukazuje na <strong>prvo lice jednine (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">yo</span>)</strong>.</p>\n<p>Ako odgovara u trećem licu, glagol bi bio <span class=\"highlighted-text\">trabaja</span>. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Elena trabaja en el departamento de diseño y experiencia de usuario.</span> - Elena radi u odeljenju za dizajn i korisničko iskustvo.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte zvuk i odgovorite na pitanje ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-asking-about-a-company/task-4"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Da li je istina ili nije istina: Elena odgovara u trećem licu.</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Istina</p>","feedback":"<p>Pažljivo saslušaj završetak glagola. Treće lice bi koristilo drugačiji oblik glagola.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Da li je stvarno</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-roof.png","characters":[{"character":"Sebastián","position":{"x":-25,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null},{"character":"Elena","position":{"x":125,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_sebastian_asks_elena_about_her_company.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":24.9,"finishTimestamp":33.64},"alwaysShowDialogue":false},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Sebastián","position":{"x":25,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Elena","position":{"x":70,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":0.5,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Sebastián","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":3.12,"dialogue":{"text":"¿En qué departamento trabajas?","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Elena","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":4.34,"finishTime":9.46,"dialogue":{"text":"Trabajo en el departamento de diseño y experiencia de usuario.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Elena","position":{"x":125,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":9.96,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Sebastián","position":{"x":-25,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":10.46,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 4","transc